Ms. H. Thi Hong, born in 1954 (Ms 23060023); amount of loan requesting is 300 USD to raise pigs & chickens. She lives with her husband and 2 children. Her 2 children are both employed and paid monthly. Her family's average income is 246 USD. In addition to raising livestock, she also tries to find miscellaneous work, such as helping out or delivering for others, to supplement her income. Because their income is still tight, she and her husband always try to work hard and hope that they can obtain the loan to expand their business and improve their livelihood. 

